          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Arbitration Fairness for Consumers Act</b></p> <p>This bill prohibits a predispute arbitration agreement from being valid or enforceable if it requires arbitration of a dispute related to a consumer financial product or service.</p>]]></text>
